{"tid":51294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本工廠拍製新入社員成長史月曆招募年輕人入行","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T02:22:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62b4a15c474a19dabb3786deac52b803bfb51dba","tid":51294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya2.jpg&h=3d223a3b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本的工業零件製造商 Ohmiya 今年推出了可愛少女月曆，請來 21 歲模特兒肉球あやと扮演工廠新人，拍攝 2017 年月曆，售價為 JYP2,400，約 HKD160，數量限定，可於官方網站購買。 <br />\n<br />\n製造商指，現今的製造工廠比起 1980 年減少了 30%，工人也由於減少 25% 而出現人手不足的情況，人們覺得成為工廠工人會很辛苦、工作環境危險等印象，也是缺乏新血的原因，強調現今的工廠其實比以前改進很多，已成為一個舒適的工作環境，因此希望通過這種宣傳來吸引年輕人加入。 <br />\n<br />\n月曆照片主題是「新入社員成長史」，從一月份的面試階段，以普通文職開始、到十二月已經完全掌握工廠運作為題，大家可以看看部份照片。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya9.png&h=1dd52e73&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya3.jpg&h=f1883aa5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya4.jpg&h=fb4d33bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya6.jpg&h=b96834c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya1.jpg&h=b3ad3dd8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya5.jpg&h=37e73322&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya7.jpg&h=75c2345f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ohmiya8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fohmiya8.jpg&h=ace226f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbc37cf692afdb5f176d2ee269292bccab0cd154","tid":51294,"uid":44970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73772e3a731c527c4d1cdb4768d544778d10e9d5","tid":51294,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"每月廿五萬yen邊個做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fa344221b5a5c8460bfacb984eef34e9d67928","tid":51294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d7aed3b00f2e9d31af1731d6a8da10849b1b6a","tid":51294,"uid":59777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:36:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"dfc587674dd1e8e9a41b0c791a0dc83d903a0927","tid":51294,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike